[Written in Draconic, one may be able to read them:]

"A gift, albeit a small one.

Though I can see in to the future, I do not see if I shall ever have a mate.

This stone has been placed, a marker of the end of legacy.

For those who gaze upon it, know this:

Your children are a reflection of your own actions."
There appears to be a small travesable crevice here big enough for a medium-sized humanoid to fit through...
